longBusinessSummary: Hello Pal International Inc. develops, markets, owns, and operates an international social networking platform in Asia. The company's Hello Pal Platform enables users to find and interact with users from all over the world through various means, such as chat messaging, livestreaming, and audio/video calling. Its platform also offers crypto-mining services. The company was formerly known as Neoteck Solutions Inc. and changed its name to Hello Pal International Inc. in May 2016. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
